reviewText: Theresa Andersson demonstrates just how far someone can take recording phrases and loops while performing live in front of an audience.  To me, she has set the bar for using these loop station devices in a live performance.  Her vocals are superb, and she is both a master multi-instrumentalist and entertainer.  I love watching this video.
She is very talented a control freak maybe, truly talented.  My wife and I are amazed at her talent.  It takes a lot of skill to be a one woman band.
